    "This has therapeutic implications as well.",
    "By analyzing ocular responses to specific virtual stimuli, therapeutic strategies can be optimized for conditions such as Post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD) or specific phobias (Diemer et al. 2023; Fehlmann et al. 2023).",
